name: Cube Run (CursedWarrior)
description:
Cube Run Game

When Running the Game, You will start in the Main Menu and by pressing on  the "Start" Button you can choose a level that you want to play.

I Reccomend Starting off with the tutorial and then then going on to the Next Level after finishing the last.

Game Instructions/ Keys :

A/D to Move left and right

Space to Restart Current Level
